summary: A little more cool texture for Daedric swords
descriptionHtml:
Found the textures of the Daedricswords, a bit dull.
Have me a little busy with Photoshop and then came out here.

Easy to copy the folder as shown below (ready)
\\The Elder Scrolls V Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\daedric

A big thank you to zanazaar that I could use the textures from it.

The original can be found here
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10274
author: Dreamdancer210
